{"@class": "com.nd.elearning.sdk.resource.gateway.v5.bean.question.QuestionVo", "original_type": 4, "original_sub_type": "questions", "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878", "id": "f0d3479b-8a69-49a1-9f2d-4bfec93eef85", "type": 201, "content": {"preview": {"question_big": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/f0d3479b-8a69-49a1-9f2d-4bfec93eef85@1.pkg/1772602115565/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772602116219", "question_small": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/f0d3479b-8a69-49a1-9f2d-4bfec93eef85@1.pkg/1772602115565/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772602116219"}, "identifier": "f0d3479b-8a69-49a1-9f2d-4bfec93eef85", "feedbacks": [{"identifier": "showHint", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": ""}, {"identifier": "showAnswer", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": "<p>A项“弃至身”应为“弃置身”；C项“沉舟测畔”应为“沉舟侧畔”；D项“长精伸”应为“长精神”。</p>\n"}], "sequnce_number": 1, "description": "<p>下列诗句中加点字的字形完全正确的一项是（ &nbsp;）</p>\n", "title": "下列诗句中加点字的字形完全正确的一项是（  ）", "res_type": "$RE0201", "adaptive": false, "timer": {"timer_type": "sequence"}, "time_dependent": false, "responses": [{"identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "1-1", "base_type": "identifier", "cardinality": "single", "corrects": ["B"]}], "location": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/f0d3479b-8a69-49a1-9f2d-4bfec93eef85@1.pkg/item.json?v=1751626612925", "items": [{"min_choices": 0, "attachments": [], "columns": 1, "type": "choice", "choices_list": [], "associable_hotspots": [], "children": [], "hide_answer_area": false, "options": [], "orientation": 0, "multiple": false, "raw": false, "titles": [], "rows": 1, "response_identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "0", "max_choices": 1, "gap_imgs": [], "choice_type": "character", "shuffle": false, "choices": [{"identifier": "A", "correct": false, "match_max": 1, "group_id": "", "fixed": false, "text": "<p>巴山楚水凄凉地，二十三年弃至身。</p>\n"}, {"identifier": "B", "correct": false, "match_max": 1, "group_id": "", "fixed": false, "text": "<p>怀旧空吟闻笛赋，到乡翻似烂柯人。</p>\n"}, {"identifier": "C", "correct": false, "match_max": 1, "group_id": "", "fixed": false, "text": "<p>沉舟测畔千帆过，病树前头万木春。</p>\n"}, {"identifier": "D", "correct": false, "match_max": 1, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<p>今日听君歌一曲，暂凭杯酒长精伸。</p>\n"}], "prompt": "<p>下列诗句中加点字的字形完全正确的一项是（ &nbsp;）</p>\n", "object": {"data": "", "width": "1000", "type": "image/png", "params": {"originalImage": "", "blankImage": ""}, "height": "600"}}], "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878"}, "source": {"container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878", "tags": ["$M002000000", "44bee8bc-54e6-11ed-9c34-850ba61fa9f4", "6a749654-0772-11ed-ac74-092ab92074e6", "44bec0c6-54e6-11ed-9c34-850ba61fa9f4", "5036342747", "$RE0000", "$M003002000", "ff8080814371757b014390f883db0453", "$RE0200", "$RE0201", "e7bbce2c-0590-11ed-9c79-92fc3b3249d5", "44bee8bc-54e6-11ed-9c34-850ba61fa9f4", "6a749654-0772-11ed-ac74-092ab92074e6", "44bec0c6-54e6-11ed-9c34-850ba61fa9f4", "ff8080814371757b014390f883db0453", "e7bbce2c-0590-11ed-9c79-92fc3b3249d5"], "status": "ONLINE", "is_publish": false, "id": "f0d3479b-8a69-49a1-9f2d-4bfec93eef85", "global_title": {"zh-CN": "下列诗句中加点字的字形完全正确的一项是（  ）"}, "global_description": {"zh-CN": "<p>下列诗句中加点字的字形完全正确的一项是（ &nbsp;）</p>\n"}, "global_keywords": {}, "global_label": {}, "custom_properties": {"sys_packing_status": "ready", "preview": {"question_big": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/f0d3479b-8a69-49a1-9f2d-4bfec93eef85@1.pkg/1772602115565/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772602116219", "question_small": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/f0d3479b-8a69-49a1-9f2d-4bfec93eef85@1.pkg/1772602115565/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772602116219"}, "auto_fill_thumb": true, "prom_resouce_type": "questions", "qb_year": "2025", "nature": "tm_sync", "audit_